{"tid":1821928,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《Happy Together》Red Velvet Joy自爆患軀體化障礙症！病由心生太讓人心疼了ㅠㅠ","createTime":"2020-01-12T15:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T04:07:30.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e2a10070fc3e6f3ccebc31432c287db5e4414d73","tid":1821928,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T15:41:04.000Z","msg":"Red Velvet出道7年，站上了K-POP巔峰的她們可想背後付出的艱辛有多大。 Joy最近錄製《Happy Together 4》時透露自己得了「火病」（軀體化障礙症、鬱火症），因為心理、情緒問題而導致身體不適，讓粉絲們十分心疼。<br />\n<br />\n「火病」這是一種「病由心生」的疾病，也是朝鮮民族特有的文化遺存綜合症，是一種患者因在生活中遭遇苦惱、壓力等卻無處發洩而出現的精神疾病。 心理上的負面情緒如緊張、壓力感太強，影響身體也跟著出現不適，但通常檢查不出明確病因。<br />\n<br />\nJoy自爆之後就有粉絲想起之前某場商務工作上，前臺突然放起了煙花，Joy嚇了一跳，立刻慌慌張張跑下臺躲起來，網友猜測那時Joy應該已經患有此病了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/XymvcVsF46SEAHlPuj/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FXymvcVsF46SEAHlPuj%2Fgiphy.gif&h=c5a97261&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/123376\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F123376&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXdArZVC5vK90EjT5EVN%2FGu4%3D&h=addc2f6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/123376</a>"},{"pid":"6c3e14b3864596447321a364323be93140a829b0","tid":1821928,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T15:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/e4b06a60c6fb063111b33ac47aab5d11/a35a5a9dab012f31-ae/s500x750/40cfdace345142f0db92b0c80a848b93a9894ca5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fe4b06a60c6fb063111b33ac47aab5d11%2Fa35a5a9dab012f31-ae%2Fs500x750%2F40cfdace345142f0db92b0c80a848b93a9894ca5.gif&h=64a436f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n牙災依家先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0722adfaa8a88cecd61